quran[38]{c,v,t}:
  56,1,Pamene ola la chiweruzo lidza
  56,2,Ndipo palibe mzimu umene udzakana kudza kwake
  56,3,Kutsitsa gulu lina ndikukweza gulu linzake
  56,4,Pamene dziko lidzagwedezeka ndi chigwedezo choopsya
  56,5,Ndi pamene mapiri adzafumbutuka kukhala fumbi lokhalokha
  56,6,Motero iwo adzakhala fumbi louluzika paliponse
  56,7,Ndipo inu mudzagawidwa m’magulu atatu
  56,8,Iwo a ku dzanja la manja. Kodi a ku dzanja la manja adzakhala ndani
  56,9,Iwo akudzanja la mazere. Kodi akudzanja la mazere adzakhala ndani
  56,10,Ndipo gulu la iwo amene adzakhala kutsogolo m’chikhulupiriro adzakhala kutsogolo m’moyo umene uli nkudza
  56,11,Awa ndiwo amene adzakhala kufupi ndi Mulungu
  56,12,M’minda ya Paradiso
  56,13,Gulu lalikulu lidzachokera ku mibadwo ya kale
  56,14,Ndi gulu lochepa lidzachokera ku mibadwo ya m’mbuyo mwake
  56,15,Iwo adzakhala pa mipando yawofowofo yomatidwa golide ndi miyala ya mtengo wapatali
  56,16,Atakhala pa iyo ndi kumayang’anizana
  56,17,Iwo adzatumikiridwa ndi anyamata a muyaya
  56,18,"Ndi mabakuli, miphika ndi zikho za vinyo wabwino"
  56,19,Amene sadzawawitsa mitu yawo kapena kuwatopetsa
  56,20,Ndi zipatso zimene adzasankhepo
  56,21,Ndi nyama ya nkhuku imene angafune
  56,22,"Ndipo padzakhala anzawo okongola, a maso akulu ndi ochititsa kaso"
  56,23,Monga ndolo zosamalidwa bwino
  56,24,Malipiro a ntchito zimene adachita kale
  56,25,Palibe nkhani zopanda pake kapena zolaula zimene adzamva
  56,26,"Kupatula mawu akuti Mtendere, Mtendere"
  56,27,"Iwo a kudzanja lamanja, kodi akudzanja lamanja adzakhala ndani"
  56,28,Iwo adzakhala pakati pa m’mithunzi ya mitengo ya Sidrah
  56,29,Ndi m’mapata a nthochi zokhala ndi mikoko wina pamwamba pa unzake
  56,30,M’mithunzi yotambasuka
  56,31,Pambali pa madzi osefukira
  56,32,Ndi zipatso zochuluka
  56,33,Zimene nyengo yake sikutha ndipo kuchuluka kwake kudzakhalabe
  56,34,Ndi pa mipando yawofowofo yokwezedwa
  56,35,Ndithudi Ife tawalenga iwo mu chilengedwe cha padera
  56,36,Ndi kuwapanga kukhala a Namwali abwino
  56,37,A chikondi pa anzawo olingana nawo zaka
  56,38,A iwo amene adzakhala kudzanja lamanja